e skin and comes with a bamboo handle.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p><p><br></p></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1585606134114" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1585606134114"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Row" id="r-1585606217579" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1585606217579" data-extraclass=""><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1543568570869" data-id="1543568570869" style="min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1585606217686" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1585606217686"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""></div></div><div data-label="Heading" id="e-1585606217616" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1585606217616"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1>11.&nbsp;<a href="https://www.theveganwarehouse.com/collections/beauty-1/products/hand-balm-gifting-set" class="">Hand Balm Gifting Set </a></h1></div></div><div data-label="Image" id="e-1585606217650" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1" data-id="1585606217650"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><a href="https://thetinyherbivore.com/2019/09/25/roasted-butternut-squash-soup-vegan/" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/7275553f-eec5-49ba-a69f-621400e1250b/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/" alt="https://www.theveganwarehouse.com/collections/beauty-1/products/hand-balm-gifting-set" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en"></a></div></div><div data-label="Text Block